articles.author: ABC News
articles.title: Russian and European astronauts make rare spacewalk - ABC News
articles.description: A Russian and a European work side-by-side outside of the International Space Station for seven hours to complete a spacewalk mission.
articles.content:
Two astronauts  one European and one Russian  ventured outside of the International Space Station (ISS) on Thursday for a seven-hour spacewalk.
